{
  "stem": "2620.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I never saw him again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I don't know whether he remained alive or not.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So anyway, that, that false liberation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I ran back to the boxcar, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they took all the dead and wounded, threw them in in one car, and we kept on going again.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We kept on going again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then the train stops again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What's happening now?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "What's happening now?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they said the Red Cross is going to give you guys soup.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We are going to let out one boxcar at a time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So everybody is waiting for their turn, you know, that they're-- and all of a sudden, there were planes attacking us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the people-- Bombs falling?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not bombs, machine gunning.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was the American planes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You see, what happened is that they had an artillery connected to the end of the train.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they thought it was the soldiers, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was an army train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were-- so the people who were down below, getting the soup-- so they opened up the boxcars for us, so we can run for cover.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, everybody got so confused.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We would start running.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so the SS was shooting from down below and the planes were shooting from up above.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was, again, a big mess.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "A lot of people died.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "A lot of people died.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And what I did is I jumped underneath, you know, underneath the train, my boxcar.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the planes were machine gunning and I can see the rails-- it was hitting the rails, so I pulled on this side.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Then it came from this side, I pulled-- oh my goodness.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This is going to be it.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
